Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Advantage Realty - HAPPY JACK
REALTY EXECUTIVES ARIZONA TERRITORY - HAPPY JACK

data.description: This almost 5 acres lot offers it all!  Great for a contractor with equipment, NO HOA, huge drive thru 3 bay detached garage, horse corral area, covd carport for your boat, tractor etc.  There are several outbuildings for all your needs, area for your RVs, toys and more. Single level, split floor plan, open floor plan, attached garage has an office area and addl bathroom.  Beautiful trees in a secluded area, sit on your decks and watch the wildlife.  Property has an electronic gate and a lot of parking and more. You must see and walk the property to appreciate everything it has to offer.
